                        <h1 class="display-4">
                            Get your <strong>portraits</strong> and other artworks done in <strong>high quality</strong>
                        </h1>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-row p-2">
                            <div class="align-self-start">
                                <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-3 lead align-self-end">For great works of art! Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nemo, provident!</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-row p-2">
