                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-3 lead align-self-end">For great works of art! Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Facere, porro?</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-row p-2">
                            <div class="align-self-start">
