                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-3 align-self-end">For great works of art! Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nemo, provident!</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-row p-2">
                        <div class="align-self-start">
